  "text": "• Learning from private data: Dehghani et al. [CITATION_1] proposed to share a model trained on sensitive private data, instead of sharing the data itself. Although this should be done in caution due to various membership attacks, see [CITATION_2] , the shared model can be used as the weak labeler.",
